article.headline: Phillips scores 24 as UNC Wilmington knocks off North Carolina A&T 73-54
article.description: — Shykeim Phillips had 24 points in UNC Wilmington's 73-54 victory over North Carolina A&T on Thursday night.
article.linkText: Phillips scores 24 as UNC Wilmington knocks off North Carolina A&T 73-54
article.story: WILMINGTON, N.C. -- — Shykeim Phillips had 24 points in UNC Wilmington's 73-54 victory over North Carolina A&T on Thursday night. Phillips also added six assists for the Seahawks (19-6, 10-3 Coastal Athletic Association). KJ Jenkins scored 12 points, finishing 4 of 7 from 3-point range. Maleeck Harden-Hayes was 4 of 10 shooting (2 for 4 from 3-point range) to finish with 12 points. Camian Shell led the Aggies (7-19, 5-8) in scoring, finishing with 21 points and two steals. Jalal McKie added 11 points and six rebounds and Jason Murphy finished with 10 points and six rebounds. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
